This website is a bit hard to understand.  So, here's some info on how to make edits!


Choosing a theme / content:
====================
_config.php - defines the current theme / content
content/* - defines all available content
_themes/* - defines all available themes


Editing content:
====================
_content/* - defines content, by theme.
_content/[theme]/[page].[part].xhtml - edit these files to add content, or add new [page]
  parts include:
  head - inside the <head> tag
  body - inside the html <body> tag
  sidebar - special section on the side fo the content, within the <body> tag
  template.body.html - original HTML page that entire website is created from


Adding new webpages:
====================
duplicate a php
add content [page].[head/body/sidebar].xhtml



Adding new photos to the homepage:
====================


Editing themes:
====================
_themes/[theme]/[page].tpl - template files for the different page types
  tempates include:
  content.tpl
  counter.tpl
  footer.tpl
  header.tpl
  index.tpl
  sidebar.tpl
  template.sidebar.tpl

